Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西怪怪的  我不知為啥有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥我正看著一點關係都沒有的同縣選手的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又不知為啥覺得差不多春日要搞點事出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點整全員在車站前集合  老老實實地過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一句話都沒說上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你說帶東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳裝  還有足夠的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…騎自行車過去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是啊  你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到的話  要請客的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才為什麼會說出自行車的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一球能上壘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣…放哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就這樣繳槍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  多拿出點幹勁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  全都到齊了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這準備的架勢來看也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏天要有夏天的樣子  不能不做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就要行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個只有一次的高一的暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿虛  你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便我們是用自行車去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你們的自行車停哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  自行車只有你和我的兩輛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那個  也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 阿虛 可不能輸給古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  出發…立即！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼！羅剎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿虛  接下來是要玩啊你怎麼就筋疲力盡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的錯啊  誰的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這人群  這消毒液的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真給人一種實在的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕快把行李放在一邊占上地方去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就看不見那些禁止跳水的文字說明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫溫的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  有希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還站著幹什麼  快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  不理她的話又該吵個不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那麼  涼宮同學  請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等…不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  還真讓人感到和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我說的是涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得她也學會了有常識性的娛樂方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打個電話過來  單方面地說有事就掛的邀請方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不能說得上是常識性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那點事  要我說根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那麼開心的涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會做什麼震動這個世界的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  大概是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春以來發生了種種事情的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得有點神經質了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是市民泳池  倒應該是平民泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  原來在那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  她一個人在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？是啥  這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這種景象以前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像也見過這樣的長門…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說起來  之後她似乎便會說出這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個就是我的團員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼他們都會聽的  所以隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吩咐他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要參加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難道具有預知能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  阿虛  皮球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好像也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  偶然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事了  既視感什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮了下今後的活動計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘不多的暑假該如何度過的預定表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在不到兩週內搞完這個嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要在不到兩週內搞完這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  有什麼想要做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想撈金魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天開始實行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近什麼地方有盂蘭盆會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煙花匯演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭再聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是實玖瑠的強烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付錢的又是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚的要請客我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天就此解散  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…我什麼事也沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近如何  精神好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  僅此而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  叫住了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  為什麼我會去搭腔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  春日的電話又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說找到盂蘭盆會的會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是今晚在市民運動場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢…唔哦哦哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  是我給挑選的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐…贊  真贊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…關鍵的東西在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  總覺得最近好像來過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個樓塔  那個店鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有看過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  那邊你想要玩的撈金魚也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撈個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼…涼宮同學  請等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個來  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那種東西有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥有種受她照顧的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西由我來買就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們不需要那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我和實玖瑠就一人拿了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  只吃一個的話沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  你那面具哪裡弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來玩煙花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  雖然極力想要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情卻讓我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  雖說玩也沒問題  你暑假作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業？那種東西三天不就全部做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種麻煩事就得事先趕緊收拾掉再玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是正確的享受暑假的方法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天真是太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  明天去捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只能捉蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團內捉蟬大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是個讓人有種「連這也是啊」的感覺的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團內捉蟬大戰就在這天開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說大家都努力奮鬥過了  可應該說不出所料還是說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然捕捉再放生的精神還是要有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它們一條生路  以後說不定會來報恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想向餘命無多的蟬要些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點像打開了盒子的潘多拉的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  不知為啥我們在一無所知的情況下  被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超市的門口做發氣球的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可算是理解除去裝甲的Virtue的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這待遇差算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長大叔也謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在實玖瑠的份上說送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就為了這種東西累死累活地幹活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它放在社團室做紀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你想什麼時候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  奪去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:12:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了不好的事情…這樣下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會跟朝比奈學姐在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點情況啊  你能現在能過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去  馬上就去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未  未…未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  事情是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在永久地重複著同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你滿面春光地把那種非現實的話說出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  沒有比現在更清楚的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才和朝比奈學姐談了下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊  這麼美的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後意識到最近這裡時間的流動出現了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該說是朝比奈學姐的功績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託她的福我也確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確信什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們似乎已經重複體驗同樣的時間許多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才就聽你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說應該是八月十七日到三十一日之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處於一個沒有盡頭的暑假的正當中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在確實是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對無法結束的Endless Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:15:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個世界裡  九月一日之後的時間全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐無法回到未來也是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物理性的沒有未來哪裡理所當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要誰相信那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們被困在那個叫什麼封閉空間裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的時間被分割開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四時整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的過程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是關於時間這個那個了的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然未來人也混進來了  那我覺得也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這件事和朝比奈學姐沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是涼宮同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然本人沒有這個自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心裡什麼地方總在想著暑假不要結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊  難道留著什麼遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她是想著暑假還有什麼事情剩下沒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了這個的話  問題就能迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像樂在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近頻繁發生的既視感之謎終於解開了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  莫非全世界的人都感覺得到這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有和涼宮同學親近的人才能感覺到這份異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙多少有一點意識到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  別說是既視感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該有一個人保存著所有輪迴中的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話可真讓人沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說也該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是超越了時空的情報統合思念體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得也許是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全都記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶問下  這重複…現在到底幾次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是第15513次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15513？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15513是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你在說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那話是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的次數  我們全都在重複同樣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15513次中沒有去盂蘭盆會的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的這兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂蘭盆會而沒有撈金魚的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9031次  其內容有6個不同的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了發放氣球  還有搬貨物  收銀  發送傳單  接電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15513次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門她這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上兩週的話就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是594年的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長的時間僅她一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠好好地保留著記憶  無數次無數次地重複嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你到底到現在為止都是什麼樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在地下的生活著的害羞人種
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是一群很友好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我看夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能搞清楚的話  問題也就迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  試下這樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面突然抱住涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳邊輕語「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由誰來做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你以外  有沒有適合的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕權發動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說不做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來做怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的了  我做這角色還不夠格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會讓涼宮同學增加多餘的混亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  長門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在朝比奈學姐說出來之前  就注意到了這輪迴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的任務是觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！快看  本壘打哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在活動來活動去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去了真正的煙花匯演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還去了釣蝦虎魚大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外還有試膽  海水浴  保齡球  卡拉OK  電影連看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我覺得春日應該不會這樣就滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此也沒有什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  只有暑假剩餘的日子是確實在一天天減少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後終於來到了  八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣課題就如實地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  各位  還有什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假已經做了好多事了  已經很充實了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還沒有滿足才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當預備日先空下來了  大家就這樣休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天在社團教室再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  如果你就這樣回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重複了一萬幾千次的兩星期又要陷入永遠循環的窘境了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我該做什麼呢  應該說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的話裡  應該有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業  還沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎麼都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重複的話  作業做了也沒意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天來不來  到時候就交給那時的我算啦


